00:45:48.650 --> 00:45:50.330
So how do I choose?

00:45:52.970 --> 00:45:56.420
How do I vote what
percentage of my care

00:45:56.420 --> 00:45:59.060
I want to send each group?

00:45:59.060 --> 00:46:01.638
[INAUDIBLE]

00:46:01.638 --> 00:46:03.680
RICHARD SCHMALENSEE: I
