make products safety

00:54:27.520 --> 00:54:28.840
regulation interest groups?

00:54:28.840 --> 00:54:30.560
Not too easily.

00:54:30.560 --> 00:54:32.320
So the [? Loewy ?]
point, and you

00:54:32.320 --> 00:54:35.080
can read the text around this
to interpret this diagram,

00:54:35.080 --> 00:54:40.600
is that that doesn't always
describe politics well.

00:54:40.600 --> 00:54:43.660
I'm going to come back to that
when we talk about regulation.

00:54:43.660 --> 00:54:45.340
There's also other models.

