Clean Air Act of 1970
was a strong assertion

01:04:08.200 --> 01:04:10.250
of federal power
over the environment.

01:04:10.250 --> 01:04:13.510
It in effect-- didn't quite,
but in effect-- created EPA.

01:04:16.260 --> 01:04:20.280
Put in the architecture for
air pollution control, water

01:04:20.280 --> 01:04:21.240
pollution control--

01:04:21.240 --> 01:04:22.890
well, the air
pollution control--

01:04:22.890 --> 01:04:25.140
that still governs.

01:04:25.140 --> 01:04:27.720
Took power from the states.

01:04:27.720 --> 01:04:29.393
Interest group competition?

01:04:34.130 --> 01:04:34.936
Brendan.

01:04:34.936 --> 01:04:36.610
AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE]
competition

01:04:36.610 --> 01:04:40.990
between environmentalists
and those maybe people who

01:04:40.990 --> 01:04:42.615
