that the Clean Air

01:04:42.615 --> 01:04:46.000
Act was [INAUDIBLE] against?

01:04:46.000 --> 01:04:47.969
RICHARD SCHMALENSEE:
Well, environmentalists--

01:04:52.960 --> 01:04:56.020
let me push you
a little farther.

01:04:56.020 --> 01:05:01.150
